<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>upload<sp/>from<sp/>local<sp/>file</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">blobClient.UploadFrom(localFilePath);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>or<sp/>upload<sp/>from<sp/>memory<sp/>buffer</highlight></codeline>
